data.description: Welcome to this 3 bedroom, 3 bath home that is truly a gem with its unique layout featuring two master bedrooms. Perfect for families or those who enjoy having extra space for guests. The vaulted ceilings in this home add a touch of elegance and create an open and airy atmosphere, making the space feel even more spacious and inviting. Kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, pantry and overlooks dining area and living room. Bamboo hardwood floors throughout, tile in bathrooms and kitchen and carpet in bedrooms. Large fenced yard and walking distance to Brookwood Park where they have storm shelters, playground and walking track
